# Environment variables for simple-svelte-todo-mvp
# -------------------------------------------------
# Define environment-specific variables here using KEY=VALUE format.
# Variables prefixed with VITE_ will be exposed to the client-side bundle via import.meta.env.
# Non-prefixed variables are typically only available during the build process (Node.js).
#
# Example (Uncomment and set if needed later):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080/api
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/database